(11, 1, 47, 3, 6, 4, null, 99, null, '<p>In 2 Cor 3:6-11, Wassung thinks Paul is juxtaposing the old covenant with the new covenant, not the old covenant with Christianity.</p> <p>Hmm.</p>'),
