(11, 1, 48, 6, 16, 4, 'The &ldquo;Israel of God&rdquo; is Israel.<br /> ..<em>maybe not</em>.', 99, '2023-02-07 04:29:29', '<p><strong>&ldquo;the Israel of God.&rdquo;</strong> The Israel of God is ... Israel. This is not a metaphor for the Christian church.</p> <p><span style="color:#E74C3C;">Per Wassung.. I think I agree.</span></p> <p>not so sure, now<span style="color:#E74C3C;">. Bob&rsquo;s not right on everything.</span></p>'),
(11, 1, 49, 1, 14, 2, null, 99, null, '<p><strong>&ldquo;the guarantee of our inheritance.&rdquo;</strong> Salvation is permanent!</p>'),
(11, 1, 49, 2, 14, 0, null, 99, '2021-10-26 18:24:18', '<p>John added the words &ldquo;He made the hostility&mdash; &ldquo;. Where did those words come from? Are they in the text?</p> <p>Never mind.. He moved them from the next verse.</p>'),
