(15, 1, 46, 6, 16, 1, null, 99, null, '<p>Shows that part of the idea concerning the joining of the man and the woman in marriage is sex. Certainly the person utilizing the services of a prostitute is not doing so with the intention of marriage. But as far as the sex is concerned, they are becoming one flesh in a kind of deeply personal union. As much as people today want to say it is just casual sex, it never is. They can act like it was just casual afterwards, but it so personal, so entrusting, so entwining, so emotional, that people are affected by it in big ways for a long time.</p> <p>Parents care for their children that their hearts not be abused. We want them to be pure and to have pure consciences before God and themselves. Parents want to protect their children and help them in every way that we can. When children sneak off and have sex it dishonors the parents.</p>'),
(15, 1, 46, 13, 8, 1, null, 99, '2023-01-14 22:32:49', null),
