(20, 0, 1, 1, 2, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-06 23:47:13', '<p>Paragah 6 links to a book with the word &quot;here&quot;. It is a technical read of 6 chapters with many more appendices. I completed all 6 chapters, but only the first 5 pages of appendix 1. (there are 21 appendices).</p> <p>It provides very detailed discussion and linguistic evidence around the gap theory.</p> <p>I am convinced that the word &quot;was&quot; should be translated &quot;became&quot; changing the translation to &quot;And the earth became formless and empty...&quot;</p> <p>Something happened there.</p>'),
(20, 0, 1, 1, 4, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-07 00:06:08', '<p>Note that this light was before the sun or moon etc.</p> <p>In the future there will be no need for the sun or moon. See Revelation 21:23 and Revelation 22:5.</p>'),
