(20, 0, 1, 1, 8, 0, null, 99, '2022-01-16 21:31:14', '<p>Further evidence the expanse is the atmosphere-note Genesis 1:20, and Genesis 1:26 and 1:28.</p>'),
(20, 0, 1, 1, 14, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-07 00:17:07', '<p>There was day and night before there were lights (sun, moon and stars), see Genesis 1:5.</p> <p>As much as we count on the sun etc, it seems it&#39;s primary job (along with the moon and other planetary bodies) is for signs, seasons and marking time.</p>'),
(20, 0, 1, 1, 15, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-07 00:21:58', '<p>See my notes on Genesis 1:4.</p>'),
(20, 0, 1, 1, 21, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-09 17:27:31', '<p>Although the word &ldquo;create&rdquo; is used here, there is no real significance to it. The Hebrew word has a wide range and could mean made or built.</p>'),
(20, 0, 1, 1, 22, 0, null, 99, '2022-01-16 21:51:40', '<p>To be fruitful and multiply is associated with God&#39;s blessing.</p>'),
