(20, 0, 1, 5, 3, 0, null, 99, '2022-05-16 06:04:42', '<p>Cain is no longer part of the lineage. Abel doesn&#39;t get a mention since being dead, he had no decendants.</p> <p>I wonder if the bigger truth points to Adam starting the lineage to Jesus, and Seth being next in line.</p>'),
