(37, 0, 19, 89, 14, 1, 'Yahweh''s standards by which He rules.', 99, '2022-04-29 15:55:32', '<p>The standard of His reign is righteousness and Justice. The essence of not blaming God for bad things. He is like a judge who presides over a case and by the standard of the law will pronounce judgement. If guilty, the perpertrator is handed over to the prison officials or as like the &ldquo;Destroyer&rdquo;, to carry out punishment.</p> <p>God as the Righteous Judge looks at the heart and lovingly extends mercy but He also limits Himself by His Word. By a free will choice the dominion over the earth was somehow legally transfered to Yahweh&rsquo;s adversay. God stays true to His act of assigning out dominion and limits His actions as he gave His word. He is faithful as to His word.</p>'),
