(37, 1, 62, 5, 19, 0, 'See 1Cor 2:7&8; Daniel 10', 99, '2022-04-10 01:30:32', '<p>I see that God has limited his power in this world because of word. Analagous to a owner of property leasing it out to a lessee therefore limiting His rights as the lessee has been given legal rights. Adam as lessee transfered rights to Satan (like a sub leasing). Now Yahweh must honor His Word in allowing Satan power over mankind. As God moves to help and direct men. Satan wars against God and men. It is a war that Satan wins some battles. The legal payment (or buy back) is the atoning sacrifice by His son as the Lamb of God.</p>'),
