(41, 1, 42, 6, 29, 1, null, 99, '2022-09-14 15:03:42', '<p>I think I disagree with the commentary, I think it is about not taking revenge, leaving revenge to God. I totally agree though with the part in the commentary that it does not mean that there should be no penalties or no justice in civil laws.</p>'),
