(41, 1, 42, 11, 20, 1, null, 99, null, '<p>The parallel passage in Matt. 12:28 says the &ldquo;spirit of God&rdquo;, this is the second place in which Holy Spirit is substituted for something else. Clearly, it is not the 3<sup>rd</sup> member in the Godhead equal with the Father. It is God&rsquo;s spirit, it is part of God, just as the finger is part of the body, not a separate God.</p>');
