(41, 1, 58, 2, 7, 2, null, 99, '2022-10-23 22:29:07', '<p>There is something interesting going on here with Gen. 1:26, this could be, in context, in Psalm 8, talking about the creation of humans, who were made a little lower than the angels, but it is also interesting that the Hebrew uses Elohim, but the Septuagint uses angelos.</p> <p>Yep, in context, it is talking about the creation of man in Genesis 1, but the author is applying it to Jesus! Crazy!</p>'),
