(49, 1, 55, 4, 13, 2, null, 99, '2022-03-12 16:14:26', '<p>Another way God has kept His Word pure is by intertwining and cross-referencing the books of the Bible and the biblical characters. With the exception of the book of Esther, every single book of the Old Testament is either quoted or referred to in the New Testament</p>'),
