(53, 0, 1, 27, 44, 0, null, 99, '2021-11-02 18:21:46', '<p>She told Jacob to be gone for &ldquo;a few days&rdquo; (Gen. 27:44), but he was gone for 20 years, and during that time Rebekah died (her death and burial are not recoerded).</p>'),
