(53, 0, 5, 32, 43, 0, 'Rejoice, O heavens, together with Him; bow down to Him, all you sons of God, for He will avenge the blood of His servants. He will return vengeance on His adversaries. He will repay those who hate Him and will make atonement for His land <em>and</em> for His people.', 99, '2022-11-02 20:25:36', '<p>Deut 32:43 Rejoice, O heavens [faithful spirit beings/angels] together with Him [Yahweh]; bow down to Him [Yahweh], all you sons of God [angels], for He [Yahweh] will avenge the blood of His servants. He [Yahweh] will return vengeance on His adversaries. He [Yahweh] will repay those who hate Him [Yahweh] and will make atonement for His land and for His people.</p>'),
