(53, 0, 19, 58, 9, 0, 'God will sweep both young and old away like a whirlwind, faster than a pot heats over burning thorns. Before cooking pots can feel the <em>fire of</em> thorns burning under them as fuel, God will sweep them away like a whirlwind.<br /> &nbsp;', 99, '2022-11-30 16:39:50', null),
