(53, 1, 44, 1, 1, 0, 'Theophilus [means &ldquo;friend of God, beloved of God&rdquo;; possibly addressing an individual and all who love God]. The first account [Gospel of Luke] I wrote was about everything Jesus began to do and teach.', 99, '2022-12-07 17:42:04', null),
(53, 1, 44, 20, 28, 0, 'the flock in Holy Spirit placed you overseers, to shepherd the church of God, which He purchased with the blood of His own Son.', 99, '2022-09-25 07:24:08', null),
(53, 1, 45, 1, 20, 0, 'Rom 10:18 &amp; Ps 19:4', 99, '2022-10-13 08:46:44', '<p>Rom 10:18 But I say, &ldquo;Did they not hear?&rdquo; Indeed, they have: THEIR VOICE WENT OUT TO ALL THE EARTH, AND THEIR WORDS TO THE ENDS OF THE INHABITED WORLD. {from Ps 19:4 (ESV) Their voice goes out through all the earth, and their words to the end of the world. In them He has set a tent for the sun. (NIV) Yet their voice goes out into all the earth, their words to the ends of the world. In the heavens God has pitched a tent for the sun.</p> <p>Rom 1:19-20 because what can be known about God is visible to them, for God has made it visible to them. For since the creation of the world His invisible attributes&mdash;His eternal power and divine nature&mdash;are clearly seen, because they are understood through what He has made, so they are without excuse.</p>'),
(53, 1, 45, 7, 6, 0, 'Serve a new way in the spirit of the law, not the old way by the letter of the Law.', 99, '2022-06-08 10:26:03', null),
(53, 1, 45, 8, 1, 0, null, 99, '2021-10-30 16:11:44', '<p>Therefore [What is &ldquo;Therefore&rdquo; there for? Must look back to see why. (Romans 7 is in PARENTHISIS) so go back to Rom 6:22 But now that you have been set free from sin and have become slaves to God, the fruit you get results in holiness and in the end, life in the age to come. 23 For the wages of sin is death, but the free gift of God is life in the age to come in Christ Jesus our Lord.]Therefore, there is now no condemnation [to the Lake of Fire] for those who are in union with Christ Jesus.</p>'),
(53, 1, 45, 8, 15, 0, null, 99, '2021-10-10 15:23:55', '<p>you received a spirit of <strong>adoption [sonship]</strong>, in connection with which we cry out, &ldquo;Abba&rdquo; (Father).</p>'),
(53, 1, 45, 8, 28, 0, 'And we know that in all things God works for good with those who love Him, even those who are called according to His purpose.', 99, '2022-11-07 19:01:49', null),
(53, 1, 45, 10, 18, 0, 'Ps 19:4 (REV)', 99, '2022-10-14 10:58:12', '<p>Rom 10:18 NIV: But I ask: Did they not hear? Of course they did: <strong>&ldquo;Their voice has gone out into all the earth, their words to the ends of the world.&rdquo; [from Ps 19:4]</strong></p> <p>Ps 19:4 NIV: Yet <strong>their voice goes out into all the earth, their words to the ends of the world.</strong> In the heavens God has pitched a tent for the sun.</p> <p>(ESV) <strong>Their voice goes out through all the earth, and their words to the end of the world.</strong> In them He has set a tent for the sun.</p> <p>Rom 1:19-20 because what can be known about God is visible to them, for God has made it visible to them. For since the creation of the world His invisible attributes&mdash;His eternal power and divine nature&mdash;are clearly seen, because they are understood through what He has made, so they are without excuse.</p>');
