(74, 0, 19, 47, 9, 0, null, 99, '2021-12-18 17:33:21', '<h3>What does &ldquo;the shields of the earth&rdquo; mean? and &ldquo;everything&rdquo; belongs to God. I am curious to know why God makes a point of saying that &ldquo;the shields of the earth,&rdquo; &ldquo;belong&rdquo; to Himself?</h3>'),
(74, 1, 47, 10, 5, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:45:39', '<p>Thoughts = evil thoughts, not every single thing!</p>'),
(74, 1, 47, 10, 6, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:43:58', '<p>Who is &ldquo;playing church&rdquo; the dominent tritarians or the Biblical Uni&rsquo;s? Can the small dog take the huge dog to task?</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 2, 0, 'How was the &quot;trust&quot; or faith measured or detected, recognized etc.', 99, '2022-03-14 23:06:17', null),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 3, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:08:35', '<p>How does anyone know that the &ldquo;rest&rdquo; is the M/K?</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 6, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:12:21', '<p>what was the disobedience?</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 7, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:15:30', '<p>&ldquo;such a long time&rdquo; is that since the time of David or before until Hebrew&rsquo;s was written or for while that generation was alive or a combo or something else?</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 8, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:17:22', '<p>when did Joshua &ldquo;speak about another day/&rdquo;</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 12, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:52:32', '<p>See 2Cor15:5 &amp;6</p> <p>bad doctrine or lies (about Paul) every thought = every evil thought</p> <p>Obedience from church before justice or kicking people out. Can&rsquo;t get rid of bad doctrine or lies/liers without. having the &ldquo;fellowship-church&rdquo; in ship shape. Are we our own/ or worse enemy?</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 13, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-14 23:59:10', '<p>Word clashing? whats up with that?!</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 15, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-15 00:05:30', '<p>sympathize-empathize, they seem the same to me. like orange and orange juice. It is a little finger on a hand verses some other finger or thumb on the hand. They are differnent fingers buy a the same thing on the same hand with variation in sie and placement being the main or only difference.</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 4, 16, 0, null, 99, '2022-03-15 00:06:51', '<p>open and honest, not a swaggerfest!</p>'),
(74, 1, 58, 5, 7, 0, 'PRS=painful reverent submission=maturity=prayers answered.  There was one prayer Jesus did not get answered the way he wanted.', 99, '2022-03-22 12:45:37', '<p>humble=going to and submitting to God. praise, prayer, attitude, expectations need to be heartfeltfully communicated to God. can&rsquo;t be humble and have pride or be proud. Lord please help me purify, or sanctify my heart and life so as to reduced or eliminate my pride. Plus reduce or eliminate resistance to be humble as well. Thanks for helping me face and deal appropriately with my fear or reluctance to face or deal with any of my weaknesses.</p> <p>This can include practical application like organiational items like filing, and care for my material things. Such as having them easy to locate and utilize in a timely manner.</p> <p>And to do this with you Yahweh and Jesus and to know that you both are worthy of my developing a finer relationship with you, others and myself!</p>'),
