(342, 0, 19, 45, 6, 1, null, 99, '2023-01-11 13:26:21', '<p>&ldquo;Professor Anthony Buzzard makes the following statement: &ldquo;Most significantly, the promised Messiah was given the title God in Psalm 45:6: &lsquo;Thy throne, O God, is for ever and ever.&rsquo; In the next verse it is made clear that this &lsquo;God Messiah&rsquo; has been blessed by his God: &lsquo;Therefore God, thy God, has anointed you....&rsquo; The&rdquo;</p> <p>&mdash; The Tyranny of the Trinity: The Orthodox Cover-Up by P.R. Lackey</p>');
