(342, 1, 43, 8, 40, 4, 'Jesus describes himself as a man', 99, '2023-01-01 13:28:46', '<p>Jesus had every opportunity to say that he was God but he didn&#39;t he called himself a man. To say that Jesus Christ was other than a man would be to go against what he said about himself and since Jesus never lied what he said about himself was the truth.</p> <p>Numbers 23:19 plainly states that God is not a man nor the son of man.</p> <p>See also Hosea 11:9</p>'),
(342, 1, 43, 8, 41, 1, null, 99, '2022-12-10 14:40:57', '<p>The Jews were saying that Jesus was born out of sexual immortality, because his mother was pregnant before being married.</p>'),
