(342, 1, 47, 11, 31, 1, 'Jesus has a God', 99, '2022-12-11 23:23:51', '<p>&ldquo;Paul gives us two compelling pieces of information here: that God is the Father of Jesus, and that the Father is God to Jesus. God has no God; He is the Supreme Being. There is no being higher than He, no being who is God over Him. If Jesus has a God, he cannot be God.&rdquo;</p> <p>&mdash; &quot;Sleight Of Mind&quot; - Volume One - The Myth Of The Christian Trinity by Steven Blake<br /> &nbsp;</p>'),
