(342, 1, 49, 2, 8, 1, 'See commentary', 99, '2022-11-20 13:21:17', '<p>There is very good commentary here on what the &ldquo;this&rdquo; consists of.</p> <p>Is it the faith, the trust, or is it the salvation that is the gift? I think the commentator says it is probably both.</p>'),
(342, 1, 49, 2, 9, 1, null, 99, '2022-11-20 13:18:35', null),
