(374, 1, 45, 1, 5, 2, '&ldquo;obedience, <em>which consists in</em> faith;&rdquo; &ldquo;faith renders obedience&rdquo;<br /> &nbsp;', 99, '2023-01-04 04:58:51', null),
(374, 1, 45, 1, 12, 4, 'Paul desires to be mutually encouraged &ndash; as well so should we do to eachother through the Word', 99, '2023-01-04 05:19:40', '<p>AMP: For I long to see you so that I may share with you some spiritual gift, to strengthen and establish you; that is, that we may be mutually encouraged and comforted by each other&rsquo;s faith, both yours and mine.</p> <p><em>This has been the biggest desire of mine, to be encouraged in the Word by my husband just as I spread encouragement through the Word.</em></p> <p><em>If we put the Word on in our hearts (really cling to it) we&rsquo;ll have a response for when the need arises &ndash; to encourage each other</em></p> <p><em>James says to have the Word rooted in our hearts. If something is rooted, it becomes a part of you. Roots grow when cultivated so in order to have teh Word rooted, it has be read, practiced, preached, lived, spoken, etc.</em></p>'),
(374, 1, 45, 1, 17, 5, 'Faith to Fath', 99, '2023-01-04 05:20:42', null),
(374, 1, 45, 1, 19, 5, '&ldquo;the knowledge of God is plain to them&rdquo;', 99, '2023-01-04 05:30:35', null),
(374, 1, 45, 2, 1, 0, 'It&rsquo;s a blanket judgment but we have to judge people to a certain extent (Paul indicates)', 99, '2023-01-07 19:14:32', null),
(374, 1, 45, 2, 4, 1, 'Reminder to be paitent, show restraint, and be kind even when they&rsquo;re wrong', 99, '2023-01-07 19:26:33', '<p>See commentary</p>'),
