(374, 1, 45, 4, 18, 2, 'GREAT example of faithfulness (trusting in the face of adversity)', 99, '2023-01-07 20:13:21', '<p>Abraham &amp; Sarah were past child bearing times yet they stayed faithful (although Sarah did falter on that and convinced Abraham to lay with the servant but that child was not the lineage to David) &ndash; I find this ironic and a paralell to Adam and Eve. Eve swayed Adam to eat the fruit.</p>'),
(374, 1, 45, 4, 19, 2, null, 99, '2023-01-07 20:10:44', null),
